source:
TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_SEQ_00Qhoterl Pasol has a passion for rations.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_SEQ_00 Schwierigkeitsanpassung (Job/Klasse darf nicht gewechselt werden)

Qhoterl Pasol möchte den Grabenden Pfoten Verpflegung mitgeben.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_SEQ_01<tab>Deliver the requested items to Qhoterl Pasol.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_SEQ_01<tab>Qhoterl Pasol die gewünschte Ware bringen

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Mine splendid scorpions at the Husk)) ((Deliver the splendid scorpions to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Gather splendid wild berries at the Husk)) ((Deliver the splendid wild berries to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Spearfish a splendid piranha in the depths of Lake Tusi Mek'ta)) ((Deliver the splendid piranha to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Beim Verlorenen Juwel <var 32 ((Item)) 06E806030502 /var> finden)) ((Qhoterl Pasol <var 32 ((Item)) 03E806030502 /var> bringen)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Beim Verlorenen Juwel <var 28 ((Item)) E8060A /var> ernten)) ((Qhoterl Pasol die <var 28 ((Item)) E8060A /var> bringen)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Im Tusi Mek'ta <var 32 ((Item)) 02E806020502 /var> fangen)) ((Qhoterl Pasol <var 32 ((Item)) 03E806020502 /var> bringen)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Once we descend into the caverns, you'll appreciate that it isn't always practical to return to the surface to satisfy every bodily whim.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Grabende Pfoten sind bei Expeditionen durch Tunnel ganz schön lange unterwegs. Sie können nicht oft nach oben kommen, um Essen und Wasser zu holen.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>In light of this, I provide our workers with some rations to take with them, and I'd be grateful if you could assist me by obtaining an ingredient.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>Qhoterl will möglichst viele Lebensmittel mitgeben, damit sie gut versorgt sind. Kannst du dabei helfen, ja?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab>Scorpions are what I require─three ought to do nicely. You will find them if you search in the Husk.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab>Beim Verlorenen Juwel findest du <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27351030502 /var>. Bitte bring drei davon.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_020<tab>Wild berries are what I require─three handfuls ought to do nicely. You will find them growing in the Husk.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_020<tab>Beim Verlorenen Juwel findest du <var 28 ((Item)) F2736B0A /var>. Bitte bring drei Portionen davon.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>A piranha is what I require─just one ought to do nicely. You will find them swimming in the waters of Lake Tusi Mek'ta, but you'll need to be handy with a spear.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>Im Tusi Mek'ta leben <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27385030202 /var>. Bitte bring einen davon.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_040<tab>As they say, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var> <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, one can't work on an empty stomach─much less when one isn't down in the caverns. So please, bring me the ingredient.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_040<tab>Qhoterl zählt auf dich! Ohne dich müssen Grabende Pfoten hungern.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_SYSTEM_100_040<tab>In order to proceed with this quest, you must first complete the quest “A New Fishing Ex-spear-ience” and unlock spearfishing.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_SYSTEM_100_040<tab>Um diesen Auftrag spielen zu können, muss das Speerfischen im Auftrag „Wie ein Fischer im Wasser“ erlernt worden sein.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_100_010<tab>That's three scorpions I require, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. You will find them if you search in the Husk.
TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_100_020<tab>That's three handfuls of wild berries I require, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. You will find them growing in the Husk.
TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_100_030<tab>That's a piranha I require, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. You will find them swimming in the waters of Lake Tusi Mek'ta.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_100_030<tab>Bitte fang <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27385020502 /var> im Schlangensee Tusi Mek'ta. Kannst du nur mit Speerfischen fangen!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_050<tab>Welcome back, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var> <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. Did your procurement efforts meet with success?

TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_060<tab>Oho, such lively scorpions these are! And this one almost stung me, the cheeky fellow! But it won't be stinging anyone after I've fried it up to a crisp, oh no.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_060<tab>Oh, Skorpione sehen aber frisch aus! In Öl kross gebraten werden zu schmackhaften und haltbaren Leckerbissen!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_070<tab>Oho, such plump, juicy berries these are! I shall press them to make invigorating drinks for our workers in the event they can't readily find groundwater.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_070<tab>Oh, frische Beeren! Daraus macht Qhoterl leckeren Saft. Gibt Grabenden Pfoten Kraft!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_080<tab>Oho, such a lively piranha this is! And it almost took a bite out of me, the cheeky fellow! But it won't be biting anyone after I've cleaned out its guts and hung it up to dry, oh no.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_080<tab>Oh, ganz frisch! An Luft getrocknet wird daraus haltbarer Leckerbissen!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_090<tab>With that, I shall set about the preparations at once. My thanks for your kind assistance, good <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ106_03811_QHOTERLPASOL_000_090<tab>Qhoterl kümmert sich schnell um Zubereitung. Vielen Dank und bis bald!
